CHANGES
=======

v0.4.0
------

* Add MQTTRawPlugin for publishing raw APRS-IS strings (maximum throughput)
* Extract shared MQTT logic into MQTTPluginBase class
* Switch from orjson to standard library json for freethreaded Python support
* Add raw_topic configuration option
* Add comprehensive test suite (14 tests)

v0.3.0
------

* Switch from json to orjson for faster JSON serialization (3-10x speedup)

v0.2.0
------

* fix pep8 errors
* Got plugin working

v0.1.0
------

* Initial commit
